room_title: Escape room "Art Heist" by Great Room Escape San Diego in San Diego
room_description: The pressure is on! You have just one hour to break into the studio of your late Grandfather and famous painter Vincent, and try to locate his masterpiece. His entire estate has already gone to his latest muse, Vanessa and this painting is the last piece of his fortune and fame. If you fail, you will forfeit the masterpiece and risk going to jail! Can you and your team complete the heist before the police arrive?
